1042
01:37:51,200 --> 01:37:52,950
Udala sam se za njega.

1043
01:37:52,991 --> 01:37:54,325
Zar ti to ne razumeš?

1044
01:38:28,616 --> 01:38:29,616
Evo.

1045
01:38:31,200 --> 01:38:33,033
Uzmi ovo pre no što odeš.

1046
01:38:33,075 --> 01:38:34,158
